{"tid":1630832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一招破解風向撚/分化撚","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:07:35.000Z","uid":164420,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7598c93740bf71881471de162977e3b6e20229c7","tid":1630832,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:49:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係冷處理！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好正負皮，唔好留言，唔推唔拉。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由得班友係個post入面圍爐吹風，到時候就會現哂型<br />\n<br />\n如果咁都有人屌我呢個post，即係佢唔同意冷處理，即係佢想吹風，即係鬼！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯丫屌哂你班吹風撚分化撚老母！<br />\n<br />\n所有吹風分化五毛撚夠膽就入黎留言！必定死全家，爛jer！"},{"pid":"4ba9d21c73a330284f1244b39d0c1c18e0896914","tid":1630832,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:50:01.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"c8921a2905972a9fcd6721cd4ef7d37d88ddc2dc","tid":1630832,"uid":62623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:50:39.000Z","msg":"極重要！唔好俾趁火打劫撚有機可乘！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630661</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b5bb37c13cd28c2bb26f3032fc5c968e3b622b0d","tid":1630832,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:50:48.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"a7012eda682fa87d4a84d959a1e04f820551d506","tid":1630832,"uid":282798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:50:58.000Z","msg":"想推"},{"pid":"02a679b1c5cb514548ec0f9b5b7a4580beb8f758","tid":1630832,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:50:59.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"681e394b69fd9338e89de90b319d99ea70f34a3c","tid":1630832,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:51:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【十八區裝修指南】</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/4/viewer?mid=18qrd4aJnY-TaYsu9jxsA6yp3zlZv9bLO&amp;ll=22.37581035920343%2C114.11057920000007&amp;z=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fu%2F4%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D18qrd4aJnY-TaYsu9jxsA6yp3zlZv9bLO%26ll%3D22.37581035920343%252C114.11057920000007%26z%3D11&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6hjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=2f61ae77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/4/viewer?mid=18qrd4aJnY-TaYsu9jxsA6yp3zlZv9bLO&amp;ll=22.37581035920343%2C114.11057920000007&amp;z=11</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">18區開花 裝修手足入嚟接Job</span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630461</a>"},{"pid":"f81e2b65ed0be36b1b773f1c3f1fe37802693663","tid":1630832,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:51:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"7f7fb67cc2f069c5d0040d9fd702aeb41b725b21","tid":1630832,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:51:38.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"e3f1f459b579024fcd0538053a1108fc30acd674","tid":1630832,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:51:52.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"f17b4120df98258dc0bab11570d1f16e03018790","tid":1630832,"uid":203619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:52:06.000Z","msg":"好地地唔會分化<br />\n自己諗下想分化既係咩人<br />\n不得不提<br />\nLIHKG比人攻擊左咁多日<br />\n今日咁順暢 啲分化撚出哂黎<br />\n你話冇古怪真係你先信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61c6466a1f01c7cfbc5a3cd6cd96779e49e12c0","tid":1630832,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:52:09.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"68975c599de9091b0435dce59e68934d075106ad","tid":1630832,"uid":299913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3UgDCyr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3UgDCyr.jpg&h=6b0fe1ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有大陸人混入黑衣人，到處搞事破壞，呢招好難拆"},{"pid":"20bc93d85eee92cb5e945228d0667a5b23f654fc","tid":1630832,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:53:28.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"a48cc9dda1bafcec44061955d00c20adf28d55be","tid":1630832,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:53:47.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"a268793dd8689a17f6461ad32d0dec924e3e01a3","tid":1630832,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13